---
title: Honey-Soy Chicken & Sesame Kumara Fries with Pear Slaw & Mayonnaise
description: The devastastatingly delicious combination of garlic, honey and soy makes tender chicken thigh the superhero of this dish! Don’t
miss out on the sesame kumara fries - this sweet and crunchy accompaniment is the perfect sidekick.
